    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and high-tension 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is robust, with the VANOS system recently serviced to ensure precise variable valve timing and optimal torque delivery. Crucially, the rear subframe has been inspected and reinforced, maintaining the structural integrity of the chassis under lateral load. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics, paired with a limited-slip differential that provides excellent traction out of low-speed corners. This is a mechanically honest vehicle with a crisp Getrag gearbox and a linear power curve, perfect for the enthusiast who prioritizes atmospheric induction and balanced handling dynamics.",
