      "description": "This 2012 Porsche Cayman is a stunning example of precision engineering, presented in a timeless Guards Red. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a careful eye will notice minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with spirited weekend drives. Inside, the black leather cabin remains supple and inviting; while the driver\u2019s seat bolster shows light signs of entry wear, the dashboard and controls are pristine and fully operational. Mechanically, this vehicle has been meticulously cared for, featuring a complete service log, a smooth-shifting manual transmission, and a set of high-performance tires with plenty of tread remaining. It strikes the perfect balance for a driver seeking a reliable, high-performance sports car that has been loved and enjoyed without being hidden away in a garage.",
