      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and has been super reliable for all my daily commutes and weekend getaways. It runs like a dream and is totally ready for its next owner to take it on some new adventures! Come take a look\u2014I think you're really going to love how it handles!",
